						<h3>GET /products</h3>
						<p class="lead">Retrieves a paginated response of a list of products from your application.</p>
						<pre><code class="http">GET http://api.marketcloud.it/v0/products</code></pre>
						<h5>Request parameters</h5>
						<div class="table-responsive"><table class="table table-striped documentation">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Field</th>
          <th>Type</th>
          <th>Description</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
